What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This is a great introductory course in German. It is not a lot of work but you learn a lot.
Every time I go to this class, I meet my friends and we study German together. It is awesome.
German at Yale kicks ass. Take it. I've taken other languages here and German was by far the most enjoyable and I feel like I've learned a ton.
Take it! Great staff, well-laid out, easy to get a lot out of!
German 120 is a logical and effective extension of German 110. Highly recommended.
